## ⚠️ Important Observations

### 1. Blocking Design

* Entire system halts while waiting for GSM
* Not suitable for real-time tasks

---

### 2. No Error Recovery

* If network fails → system just retries next loop
* No reconnection logic

---

### 3. Session Not Terminated

* Intentionally kept open for performance
* Avoids reinitialization overhead

